    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, slash and dash your way through hordes of enemies and <u><strong>bosses</strong></u> using an array of face melting weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/24f0a96d8a4e7f275077970733335178.poster.avif?t=1732192005\" width=560 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/24f0a96d8a4e7f275077970733335178.webm?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/24f0a96d8a4e7f275077970733335178.mp4?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match the unlocked <strong><u>progressions</u></strong> to support your individual playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the <strong><u>procedurally generated</u></strong> levels with snappy and responsive controlls while you fight in a <strong><u>challenging</u></strong> combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/751c77593ef166308693d9c808d5cf95.poster.avif?t=1732192005\" width=560 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/751c77593ef166308693d9c808d5cf95.webm?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/751c77593ef166308693d9c808d5cf95.mp4?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awesome audio combined with whimsical visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Co-op gameplay</u></strong> upto 4 players! Experience the madness together with your friends, and see how far you can get together!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover your breath</strong> between the exhilarating levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional <strong><u>mini-games</u></strong> focused around movement, combat and breathing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/ec114d2b687e725107a71837003a6213.poster.avif?t=1732192005\" width=560 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/ec114d2b687e725107a71837003a6213.webm?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2340860/extras/ec114d2b687e725107a71837003a6213.mp4?t=1732192005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
